Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:01.35,0:00:04.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嚮往天空 親近天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.74,0:00:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,翱翔於天空的神秘力量開始被一少部分人掌握的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.45,0:00:11.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Guardian
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.85,0:00:14.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那裏有一個傳說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.15,0:00:19.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在天之邊際雲之彼方存在著一片黃金之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.32,0:00:24.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這個故事講述了一個追尋夢想自由生存的天空盜賊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.11,0:00:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,空盜團少年——酷的波瀾起伏的愛和冒險的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.84,0:02:03.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在拉茲飛·安克魯港鎮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.74,0:02:08.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷和蕾遇到了欠下巨債的拉撒蒂和莉莉雅姐妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.98,0:02:12.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拉撒蒂為了保護莉莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:12.63,0:02:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,投身於在教堂廢墟的地下深處的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.39,0:02:18.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一個秘密的鬥技場所舉辦的賭鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.53,0:02:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.30,0:02:24.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看到煌珠被當作武器在使用的希絲卡他們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.58,0:02:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,受到了十分激烈的衝擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.75,0:02:28.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,與此同時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.67,0:02:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,正要款待酷和蕾的莉莉雅遭到了幾個男人的襲擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.74,0:02:50.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣下去可不妙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.76,0:02:51.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,未知的夢境{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.24,0:02:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.62,0:02:53.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,編織在一起{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.16,0:02:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,並一直延續{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.70,0:02:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誘惑至深入{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.30,0:02:58.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,使之閉目{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.07,0:03:00.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虛幻之路{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.37,0:03:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.56,0:03:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,掃除全部{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.32,0:03:09.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,眼睛 眼睛...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.44,0:03:13.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.28,0:03:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,趁現在同契
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.28,0:03:17.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.34,0:03:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.51,0:03:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,耍陰招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.78,0:03:21.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.39,0:03:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.45,0:03:27.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幽美星夜{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.01,0:03:29.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,牽引之線{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.69,0:03:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,彼此傾心{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.42,0:03:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在天之原{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.21,0:03:34.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,追及之畏{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.10,0:03:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,深藏在心{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.52,0:03:39.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,與我共頌念{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.60,0:03:41.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,締結契約{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.05,0:03:42.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,氣息相應{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.01,0:03:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,纏繞飛旋之風{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.03,0:03:47.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,汝與我{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.61,0:03:48.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,永遠相隨{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.32,0:03:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,赤誠之心{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.07,0:03:52.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,纏繞飛揚之風{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.89,0:03:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,締結契約{\a6}
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.66,0:03:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.66,0:03:59.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是煌珠同契者啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.85,0:04:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.65,0:04:10.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第十唱 愛和慾望的賭鬥場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.96,0:04:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 這真是意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.99,0:04:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不敗的少虎拉撒蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.56,0:04:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,受到對方的攻擊後顯得很痛苦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.77,0:04:21.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.52,0:04:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還以為標榜為不敗的是個什麼樣的怪物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.37,0:04:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒用的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.67,0:04:27.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我之所以沒輸過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.06,0:04:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是因為我不能輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.99,0:04:34.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,將鬥氣集中...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.06,0:04:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,感覺像是要發動攻擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.33,0:04:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下一擊將決定勝負
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.61,0:04:47.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,狂妄的小毛孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.76,0:04:51.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不敗的名號就到此為止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.93,0:04:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我無論如何都不能輸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.24,0:04:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吼號穿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.28,0:04:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.98,0:05:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不愧是拉撒蒂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.87,0:05:11.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,將那麼巨大的對手輕易擊倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.31,0:05:13.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有兩下子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.66,0:05:16.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一擊就將和煌珠同契的同契者打倒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.22,0:05:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難以置信的威力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.11,0:05:35.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷 後面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.30,0:05:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和這樣的怪物打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.10,0:05:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,命有幾條都不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.50,0:05:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.80,0:06:01.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.74,0:06:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.64,0:06:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.04,0:06:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.39,0:06:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,莉莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.38,0:06:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,莉莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.08,0:06:47.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.47,0:06:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,昨天想擄走莉莉雅的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.17,0:06:53.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,帶著同夥來襲擊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.64,0:06:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過 總算被我們趕走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.61,0:06:58.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.10,0:07:03.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.85,0:07:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.05,0:07:08.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.51,0:07:13.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.43,0:07:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把莉莉雅留在家裏自己出去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.11,0:07:17.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.90,0:07:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.87,0:07:30.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,給你們添麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.14,0:07:32.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,承蒙照顧幫了我們很大的忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.14,0:07:34.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,應該是我們道謝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.23,0:07:36.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救了莉莉雅兩次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.90,0:07:41.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.08,0:07:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.55,0:07:45.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要遵守哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.71,0:07:48.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和那女孩的約定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們也要好好相處啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.61,0:08:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前輩真慢啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.72,0:08:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希望不要使事情複雜化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.06,0:08:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,事情有了完善的解決方案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.54,0:08:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.35,0:08:26.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,將在賭鬥場展開大規模的徹底的煌珠保護作戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.21,0:08:27.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.13,0:08:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拉茲飛·安克魯分部答應派出援軍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.32,0:08:34.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.99,0:08:38.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們要再次潛入賭鬥場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.30,0:08:39.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等待援軍到來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.24,0:08:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又要穿這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.46,0:08:45.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好嗎 龍威
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.30,0:08:46.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒想到很配你嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.71,0:08:51.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾他們怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.97,0:08:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不聯繫他們沒關係嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.00,0:08:55.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾的所在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.48,0:08:57.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可以用煌珠雷達探測到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.38,0:08:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要緊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.66,0:09:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等作戰結束後再匯合吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.06,0:09:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比起那個 問題是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.32,0:09:05.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,問題是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.82,0:09:10.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷他們有沒有在努力賺錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.02,0:09:15.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今後該怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.25,0:09:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,結果昨天我們兩個都被解雇了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.06,0:09:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是被希絲卡知道還沒賺到一分錢的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.92,0:09:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,會被殺掉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.86,0:09:33.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道就沒有能快速賺到錢的方法嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.35,0:09:35.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個的話我倒有個好辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.42,0:09:38.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.52,0:09:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我可是來告訴你好消息的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.01,0:09:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.59,0:09:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想要錢的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.40,0:09:48.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就去山崗上的教堂廢墟看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.95,0:09:51.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誰會相信你的鬼話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.74,0:09:54.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一到晚上那裏的地下就有格鬥比賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.39,0:09:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,取勝的話可以得到很多獎金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.47,0:10:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你都有這麼厲害的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.48,0:10:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也許能賺很多錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.39,0:10:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.54,0:10:07.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不想幹的話是不會逼你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.44,0:10:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別看我這樣 我可是很好心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.29,0:10:14.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,告訴你進入會場的暗號吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.62,0:10:20.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,跟在教堂廢墟的入口處的黑衣人這樣說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.70,0:10:23.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要呼喚女神 機會就會降生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.30,0:10:26.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,望著腳下之地 有著主的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.23,0:10:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嘰哩咕嚕的真囉嗦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.98,0:10:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.05,0:10:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.66,0:10:52.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是昨晚的獎金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:53.58,0:10:55.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你幹得很好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.50,0:10:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這筆錢我馬上交給那夥人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.92,0:11:03.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,昨晚好像陷入了苦戰 沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.62,0:11:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.84,0:11:09.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要太勉強了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.90,0:11:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今晚還是不要出場的好……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.74,0:11:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.69,0:11:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我還是想出場
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.23,0:11:17.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,瑪魯先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.43,0:11:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.59,0:11:21.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我要是在今晚的比賽中獲勝的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.60,0:11:25.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那獎金應該就能徹底還清父母親欠下的債
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.39,0:11:28.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那樣一來莉莉雅就能自由了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.75,0:11:32.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.24,0:11:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可以不用再擔驚受怕會被誰帶走了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.75,0:11:39.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 我想是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.82,0:11:46.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.02,0:11:58.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,莉莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.23,0:12:01.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今晚來看我的比賽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.63,0:12:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,昨晚的事也許會再發生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.34,0:12:07.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也不放心讓你一個人在家裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.90,0:12:09.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.51,0:12:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我今晚一定會贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.62,0:12:16.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後讓你獲得自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.91,0:12:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想和你分享那個瞬間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.60,0:12:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.92,0:12:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,失手了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.30,0:12:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.04,0:12:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拉撒蒂那傢伙把欠款全部還清的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.65,0:12:43.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就不能再束縛莉莉雅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.89,0:12:47.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以命令你在那之前綁架莉莉雅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.85,0:12:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒用的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.88,0:12:51.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒想到來了個攪和的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.84,0:12:53.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蹩腳的借口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.00,0:12:55.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.33,0:12:58.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是個奇怪的煌珠同契者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.10,0:13:00.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奇怪的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.96,0:13:03.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想絕對很值錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.22,0:13:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一看臉就明白……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.76,0:13:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎樣的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.30,0:13:08.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,同契者只是個小毛孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.20,0:13:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.16,0:13:11.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,煌珠倒是很厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.34,0:13:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,會變成一把巨大的劍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.48,0:13:17.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能自由自在地操控風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.50,0:13:26.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.67,0:13:28.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒人要雇我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.90,0:13:32.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真不容易啊 賺錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.84,0:13:35.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.27,0:13:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,剛才那人說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.19,0:13:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,山崗上的教堂廢墟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.07,0:13:42.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別說傻話了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.32,0:13:45.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那種人知道的肯定不是什麼好地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.14,0:13:47.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我先不說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.27,0:13:49.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼能讓蕾去冒險呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.97,0:13:55.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是沒錢的話不就去不了煌珠樂園了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.60,0:13:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.01,0:13:59.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就因為那樣 為了去那裏而讓蕾去戰鬥什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.61,0:14:04.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我說好要帶蕾去煌珠樂園的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.43,0:14:06.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.65,0:14:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我並不想要酷來保護我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.96,0:14:15.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,並不想要酷做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.95,0:14:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.25,0:14:27.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.00,0:14:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我只是想和酷在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.35,0:14:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和蕾在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.50,0:14:38.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.11,0:14:40.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.34,0:14:50.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.41,0:14:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們兩個就去搗亂一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.23,0:15:14.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要呼喚女神 機會就會降生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.68,0:15:15.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,望著腳下...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.24,0:15:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,望著腳下...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.78,0:15:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 是什麼來著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.87,0:15:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,望著腳下之地 有著主的痕跡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.74,0:15:55.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那裏幹什麼呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.34,0:16:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,倒是你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.59,0:16:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,弄成這副裝束在幹嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.86,0:16:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們是有任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.94,0:16:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,任務？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.07,0:16:12.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這裏在舉辦賭錢的格鬥賽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.24,0:16:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有很多煌珠同契者參加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.41,0:16:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難道說 酷也...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.98,0:16:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.42,0:16:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷 你這個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.64,0:16:25.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,知道我們的任務是保護煌珠 還...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.23,0:16:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這和我沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.56,0:16:30.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再說要我們賺錢的不是你嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.47,0:16:31.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但也不能因此而...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.00,0:16:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我和蕾約好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.18,0:16:37.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一起去煌珠樂園
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.00,0:16:41.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾沒意見嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.90,0:16:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在這種地方打鬥什麼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那我就當作什麼都沒看見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.14,0:16:53.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那樣才對嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.74,0:16:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.87,0:16:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒關係嗎 前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.54,0:17:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷若僅僅只是想要賺錢的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.87,0:17:05.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,蕾是不可能和他一起戰鬥的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.66,0:17:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,或許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.91,0:17:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在這裏的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.16,0:17:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無論是對於他們來說還是對於我們來說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.47,0:17:14.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,都會是找到什麼問題的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.15,0:17:16.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而且
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.15,0:17:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為了能確確實實地將這裏所有的煌珠保護起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.53,0:17:23.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,必須等待援軍的到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.56,0:17:24.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.68,0:17:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們不要讓人知道是守護翼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.22,0:17:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就當自己是客人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.21,0:17:30.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.23,0:17:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.83,0:17:34.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這裏舉行的比賽是賭錢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.04,0:17:35.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.91,0:17:36.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.00,0:17:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在那些沒勝算的傢伙身上下注
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.28,0:17:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,若是贏了的話不是能賺很多錢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.38,0:17:45.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.33,0:17:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,押在酷身上怎麼樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.04,0:17:48.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.55,0:17:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算蕾有多麼厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.73,0:17:54.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,同契者是酷的話要想贏就還...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.86,0:17:56.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.65,0:17:58.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我倒是覺得很可行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.96,0:18:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也覺得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.32,0:18:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷若是狀態不錯的話好像能超常發揮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.65,0:18:06.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能那麼順利嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.70,0:18:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這可真是驚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.19,0:18:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷德·望·朱魯愛特初次登台
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.29,0:18:22.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一擊就將對手巴狄·多拉打得喪失戰鬥力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.97,0:18:25.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們兩人聯手的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.70,0:18:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一下子就能搞定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.08,0:18:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對吧 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.68,0:18:29.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.61,0:18:31.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不愧是梅札蘭斯一族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.04,0:18:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不覺得檔次不同嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.28,0:18:37.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 蕾和酷的同步率高得驚人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.75,0:18:38.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是吧 前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.76,0:18:41.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,前輩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.98,0:18:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能實現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.81,0:18:44.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這不是在做夢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.22,0:18:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,南風之弦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.52,0:19:00.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,東風之鈽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:12.42,0:19:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不累嗎 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.60,0:19:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.21,0:19:17.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好勒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一鼓作氣贏到底
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.89,0:19:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不會錯的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.45,0:19:25.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.15,0:19:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.52,0:19:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別擔心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.91,0:19:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為了你 這點傷算不了什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.08,0:19:39.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是瑪魯先生不是說過嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.23,0:19:41.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別太勉強比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.64,0:19:44.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,傷成這樣了還要去戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.96,0:19:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不能再讓姐姐...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.50,0:19:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是說了不用擔心的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.01,0:19:51.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我今晚一定會贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.94,0:19:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贏了讓你重獲自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.75,0:19:59.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.77,0:20:01.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我真的沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.94,0:20:04.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,去鬥技場等我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.77,0:20:23.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓各位久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.69,0:20:25.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,決戰即將開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.14,0:20:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,首先介紹的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.92,0:20:31.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是第一次露面卻一口氣贏到現在的新人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.98,0:20:34.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷德·望·朱魯愛特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.66,0:20:37.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.61,0:20:41.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.70,0:20:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的全部財產都押在你身上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.21,0:20:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定要打她個落花流水 知道了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.63,0:20:50.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我說 蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.21,0:20:52.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.22,0:20:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不管對手是怎樣的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.85,0:20:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定要贏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.18,0:20:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:56.13,0:20:57.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他的對手是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.38,0:20:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們賭鬥場的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.03,0:21:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不敗的少虎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.59,0:21:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拉撒蒂·地可蕾絲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.47,0:21:07.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,酷德
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.82,0:21:12.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你原來是煌珠同契者啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.57,0:22:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,贏了這場比賽就能改變命運
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:54.22,0:22:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,凝聚數年心願的拳頭異常兇猛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.66,0:22:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,下回 復仇的賭鬥士
